title: BRIEF-North American Outreach signs deal with Cxense
text:
Oct 14 Cxense ASA :
* North American Outreach, Inc. signs deal with Cxense
* Contract includes licensing the Cxense DMP (Data Management Platform), Cxense Content (site personalization), and Cxense Maxifier (advertising optimization) products Source text for Eikon:
